reviewText: THE GOLDEN AGE OF TOY TRAINS covers the post-war toy train craze nicely.  Lionel and American Flyer are the focal points for this DVD.  Whether your favorite featured 2-rail (S Gauge) or 3-rail (O gauge) trains, this will be a pleasant stroll through bygone days for any "Baby Boomer."
My son loves this train show. Amazing! layouts. What not to love about all things train. Can watch over and over again.

If you like trains, especially the Postwar trains, you will love this DVD.

Rix

This a great dvd. Very good quality.
The price was great.
We will watch this dvd often.
Very happy with the purchase.
